        <section class="detail-section alt"><div class="detail-shell"><header class="detail-heading detail-reveal"><small>Project problem</small><h2>The Design Challenge</h2><p>Preschool and kindergarten learners need short, visually engaging, and easy-to-understand learning experiences. The challenge was to translate educational goals into mobile-game activities that remained playful without overwhelming young children with complex instructions, cluttered visuals, small controls, or difficult interactions.</p></header><div class="kopo-feature-grid challenge-card-grid">${challenge.map(x=>`<article class="kopo-mini-card challenge-card ${x[0]} detail-reveal"><i class="bi ${x[1]}"></i><h3>${x[2]}</h3><p>${x[3]}</p></article>`).join('')}</div></div></section>
